cdata.name: Arena
cdata.desc:
Arena is an eSports cryptocurrency speculation ecosystem. It is a platform where users are able to trade (buy/sell) eSports predictions and signals for digital currencies between them. At Arena, participants have the ability to develop a winning track record wich in the case of being successful, will give them the option to charge other users for the information given.

The ARENA token is an Ethereum-based (ERC-20) cryptocurrency. It is the digital asset that fuels the Arena portal, where speculators and eSports enthusiasts congregate and trade information.
